This is a Advanced chat app...mixture if "Hike" and "WhatsApp"..here if you want to chat with any person first you need to add 
him in to your own chat list...Last seen and on line feature is available, If you send a message to a user and at that time user 
is not present a notification will be send to that user that you send the message...Timeline feature is added...you can post a 
comment of anyone's post...and many more feature..
